OL,6,FA touching letter sent by the author
OL,7,Fof The Hobbit and Lord of The Rings to
OL,8,Fa little boy, 63 years ago, is
OL,9,Fexpected to spark an auction bidding
OL,10,Fbattle.
OL,12,FJ.R.R. Tolkien, the 'father of fantasy
OL,13,Fliterature' wrote to his young fan a
OL,14,Ffew days after Christmas in 1961.
OL,16,FThe treasured letter was sent to
OL,17,FChristopher Howard when he was eight-
OL,18,Fyears-old and was later placed in a
OL,19,Fkeepsake box - where it remained for
OL,20,F60 years.
