OL,3,CJRR Tolkien letter to fan expected to
OL,4,Cfetch thousands at auction
OL,6,FNow aged 71, Christopher, a renewable
OL,7,Fenergy consultant from Wye, near
OL,8,FCanterbury, Kent, has decided it is
OL,9,Ftime to send the letter on to its next
OL,10,Fdestination.
OL,12,FIt will be offered at Hertfordshire
OL,13,FAuction House Hanson Ross on 12 April
OL,14,Fwith a guide price of #8,000- #10,000.
OL,16,FHowever, it could exceed expectations
OL,17,F- in 2023 a lengthy autograph Tolkien
OL,18,Fletter, sent to his publisher,
OL,19,Fachieved a premium inclusive total of
OL,20,F$32,500 (#25,671) at auction.
