OL,6,FChristopher Howard said: "Back in 1961
OL,7,Fwe were living in the North West of
OL,8,FEngland at the curious address you can
OL,9,Fsee on the envelope, 'Asmall Lodge,
OL,10,FAsmall Lane, Ormskirk, Lancashire'.
OL,12,F"My mother was an English teacher who
OL,13,Fwould read bedtime stories to my
OL,14,Fyounger brother and I, and started
OL,15,Freading The Hobbit to us.
