OL,4,Cfetch thousands at auction
OL,6,F"The magical effect of reading words
OL,7,Fthat created pictures in my mind
OL,8,Famazed me. I could see the dragon,
OL,9,FSmaug, in his lair, the Dwarves in
OL,10,Ftheir mountain halls, Wizards, Orcs
OL,11,Fand of course, Hobbits."
OL,13,FTolkien who was living in Oxford, at
OL,14,Fthe time, and responded in a letter
OL,15,Fdated 28 December 1961.
OL,17,FMr Howard continued: "You can imagine
OL,18,Fhow thrilled I was to receive this
OL,19,Fletter. Immediately, on seeing the
OL,20,Fenvelope, in my mind.
