OL,3,CJRR Tolkien letter to fan expected to
OL,4,Cfetch thousands at auction
OL,6,F"Professor Tolkien's beautiful
OL,7,Fhandwriting transported our home
OL,8,Fstraight to Middle Earth.
OL,10,F"In his reply, he took time to
OL,11,Fcarefully address every point in my
OL,12,Fletter, referred to my younger brother
OL,13,FNicky, mentioned characters in The
OL,14,FHobbit, and informed me in detail
OL,15,Fabout the other book - or books - he
OL,16,Fhad written, The Lord Of The Rings."
OL,18,FAmanda Butler, head of operations at
OL,19,FHanson Ross, said: "It's a wonderful
OL,20,Ffind, a very touching, kind and
OL,21,Fpersonal letter.
