OL,6,F"It reminds us of the art of letter-
OL,7,Fwriting in a fast-paced world now
OL,8,Fdominated by emails and short and
OL,9,Fsnappy text or WhatsApp messages.
OL,11,F"Professor Tolkien was a busy man, and
OL,12,Fyet he found time at Christmas to
OL,13,Fwrite to a young fan. It's hard to
OL,14,Fimagine any celebrity today composing
OL,15,Fsomething so special.
