OL,3,CJRR Tolkien letter to fan expected to
OL,4,Cfetch thousands at auction
OL,6,F"The fact that our vendor has
OL,7,Ftreasured the letter for life
OL,8,Funderlines its importance. It offers
OL,9,Fus a glimpse of Tolkien's kindness and
OL,10,Fintegrity and is a welcome reminder of
OL,11,Fold-fashioned values and courtesy. We
OL,12,Fvery much hope to deliver the auction
OL,13,Fresult it deserves."
OL,15,FFrom 1925 to 1945, JRR Tolkien was the
OL,16,FRawlinson and Bosworth Professor of
OL,17,FAnglo-Saxon and a Fellow of Pembroke
OL,18,FCollege at the University of Oxford.
